OL,3,C'Violent thief jailed for following
OL,4,Celderly people home and robbing them
OL,6,FA "violent" man has been jailed for
OL,7,Feight years after he followed elderly
OL,8,Fpeople home and robbed them.
OL,10,FKiril Mihaylov, 30, of Hamilton Road,
OL,11,FLongsight was convicted for a series
OL,12,Fof robberies including one of a 96-
OL,13,Fyear-old woman, whom he followed from
OL,14,FPiccadilly Gardens to her home address
OL,15,Fin Little Hulton.
OL,17,FWhen the victim entered her home,
OL,18,FMihaylov forcibly grabbed her necklace
OL,19,Fbefore ripping it from her neck.
