OL,3,C'Violent thief jailed for following
OL,4,Celderly people home and robbing them
OL,6,FThe victim who has since died, used to
OL,7,Fenjoy travelling to the city centre
OL,8,Fusing the buses to walk and have
OL,9,Fcoffees with her friends and family.
OL,11,FOn 26 August, another 82-year-old
OL,12,Fvictim was punched in the stomach and
OL,13,Frobbed after taking a short cut
OL,14,Fwalking home from the city centre.
OL,16,FMihaylov grabbed her jewellery from
OL,17,Fround her neck and grabbed her ears to
OL,18,Ftake her earrings. In fear for her
OL,19,Flife, the victim shouted "I'll give it
OL,20,Fto you".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
