OL,3,C'Violent thief jailed for following
OL,4,Celderly people home and robbing them
OL,6,FThe day after, on 27 August, an 80-
OL,7,Fyear-old man woke up to find a man
OL,8,Fstood in his house in Salford with a
OL,9,Flarge knife in his hand, having been
OL,10,Fto the city centre during the day.
OL,12,FHe woke up at 11pm when he noticed his
OL,13,Fhigh-value watch was missing from his
OL,14,Fbedside table.
OL,16,FWhen going downstairs, he discovered
OL,17,Fthat his patio doors had been smashed
OL,18,Fand a man was stood in his property
OL,19,Fwith a large knife in his hand.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
