OL,3,C'Violent thief jailed for following
OL,4,Celderly people home and robbing them
OL,6,FThe watch belonging to the victim was
OL,7,Ffound to be in transit to Mihaylov's
OL,8,Ffamily in Bulgaria, but has since been
OL,9,Freturned to the owner by authorities.
OL,11,FDetective Inspector Micheal Sharples
OL,12,Fof Salford's Neighbourhood Crime Team,
OL,13,Fsaid: "Mihaylov's actions were
OL,14,Fcowardly, he would systematically prey
OL,15,Fon elderly people who he saw going
OL,16,Fabout their daily lives in the city
OL,17,Fcentre and would follow them home
OL,18,Fthinking they would be an easy target.
OL,26,@uD@GOU
