OL,3,C'Violent thief jailed for following
OL,4,Celderly people home and robbing them
OL,6,F"As a team, we cannot thank the
OL,7,Fvictims enough, for coming forward and
OL,8,Fsupporting our investigation. Their
OL,9,Finvolvement has helped us secure
OL,10,Fenough evidence to convict Mihaylov,
OL,11,Fand ensure he cannot harm anyone else.
OL,13,F"These incidents were particularly
OL,14,Fshocking as he targeted elderly
OL,15,Fpeople. When speaking with the
OL,16,Fvictims, we could sense just how much
OL,17,Fthey valued their independence, and
OL,18,Ftheir days out to the city centre.
OL,19,FMihaylov's actions have left them
OL,20,Fshaken and questioning their safety.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
