OL,3,C'Violent thief jailed for following
OL,4,Celderly people home and robbing them
OL,6,F"I hope that by knowing he is now
OL,7,Fbehind bars, this will provide them
OL,8,Fwith a small measure of comfort, and
OL,9,Fthat they will continue to confidently
OL,10,Fgo about their daily lives, doing what
OL,11,Fthey enjoy the most."
OL,13,FMihaylov was sentenced for eight years
OL,14,Fon Monday 3 March for two robbery
OL,15,Foffences and a residential burglary
OL,16,Foffence.
